  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Lists are powerful tools throughout RepairQ, offering features like filters, keyword search, and saving favorite list views for future use. Users can customize which columns of data are visible, ensuring that key information is readily accessible when viewing and sorting lists. This flexibility extends to exporting data, allowing users to tailor the information to their needs. Customized list views can be saved and shared with staff, enhancing convenience for everyone.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Data Management </strong>- Quickly filter, search, and access relevant information in your lists.</p></li><li><p><strong>Personalization</strong> - Customize visible columns to focus on the most important data.</p></li><li><p><strong>Collaboration</strong> - Share customized list views with your staff, ensuring consistent access to key information.</p></li></ul><p /><p>There are many List Views in RepairQ, including:</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"ba9a91f4-2cf2-484f-b444-3ca7c8b08fc9\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Ticket Queue</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Inventory Summary</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Inventory Detail</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Inventory Transfers</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Catalog</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Appointments</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Customers</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Invoices</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h3 id=\"ListViews:EditingColumns-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932427325/Catalog+Settings\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932427325\" data-linked-resource-version=\"12\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Catalog Settings Overview</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932787831/Purchase+Orders+List+View\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932787831\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Purchase Orders: List View</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932656694/Saving+and+Sharing+Custom+List+Views\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932656694\" data-linked-resource-version=\"9\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Saving and Sharing Custom List Views</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1937211440/Inventory+Detail+-+List+View+Column+Updates\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1937211440\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Inventory Detail - List View Column Updates</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933606925/Keyword+Search+Techniques\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933606925\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Keyword Search Techniques</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932754986/List+Views\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932754986\" data-linked-resource-version=\"12\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">List Views</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1993375753/Instructional%20-%200091cd.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"ListViews:EditingColumns-CustomizeListColumns\">Customize List Columns</h2><p>Navigate to any List you would like to customize. For this example, we will modify the Inventory Summary List View. On the Navigation Bar, go to <strong>Inventory </strong>\u2192 <strong>Inventory Summary</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"680\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1993375753/Edit%20Column%201.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>On the Inventory Summary screen, you can see the default columns along the top row of the list. To edit your available columns, click the <strong>Options button (\u22ee)</strong>\u00a0on the right side of the page. From the dropdown list of options, select <strong>Edit Columns</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1993375753/Edit%20Column%202.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"204\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1993375753/Edit%20Column%203.png?api=v2\"></span><h3 id=\"ListViews:EditingColumns-AddorRemoveDataColumns\">Add or Remove Data Columns</h3><p>Once in Column Edit mode, click the <strong>Add Button (+)</strong>, and the Column Edit window will appear. The <strong>Selected Columns </strong>section includes the columns that are currently on your List.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1993375753/Edit%20Column%204.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>Scroll down until you reach the <strong>Add Columns</strong> section. This section contains all the fields you can add to your Inventory Detail view. Select the <strong>checkbox next to the field(s)</strong> you wish to add to the Column List. Alternatively, you can search for the desired column(s) by typing a keyword into the category box. The pop-up will then display any columns containing that keyword.</p><p>To remove columns, uncheck the box next to the field.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1993375753/Edit%20Column%205.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1993375753/Edit%20Column%206.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>Once your list is customized, click the <strong>Finish button (checkmark)</strong> to update your list. After updating, your list will reflect the new columns.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1993375753/Edit%20Column%207.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1993375753/Edit%20Column%208.png?api=v2\"></span><h3 id=\"ListViews:EditingColumns-ChangeColumnOrder\">Change Column Order</h3><p>You can use the <strong>Edit Columns</strong> feature to reorder your columns. Click and drag each category to your desired order. Once you have changed the order to your preference, click the <strong>Finish button (checkmark)</strong> to update your list.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1993375753/Edit%20Column%209.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>Your List will now show as Default-<em>Modified</em>. If you want to save or share the new List View, check out our Knowledge Base Article, <a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932656694/Saving+and+Sharing+Custom+List+Views\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932656694\" data-linked-resource-version=\"9\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Saving and Sharing Custom List Views</a>.</p><p>If you reset the filters, your list will revert to the Default view.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1993375753/Edit%20Column%2010.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p /><p>START 1.21.X</p>",
